11
00:00:59,167 --> 00:01:01,167
Yeah, it's actually pretty tiring.

12
00:01:01,167 --> 00:01:01,767
Yeah.

13
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,400
That arrow I just shot,

14
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,267
