24
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:29,800
Calm and composed.

25
00:01:30,633 --> 00:01:32,067
Don't panic.

26
00:01:32,067 --> 00:01:33,267
Raise your bow.

27
00:01:33,567 --> 00:01:36,067
