32
00:01:47,033 --> 00:01:48,033
It's okay.

33
00:01:52,367 --> 00:01:53,367
This is my last arrow.

34
00:01:53,667 --> 00:01:55,467
Everyone at the judges' table

35
00:01:55,467 --> 00:01:56,300
